snippet.title: Wrestle Story Reveal Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Wrestle Story is a story-driven turn-based action RPG from Tictoc Games, where you play as an up-and-coming wrestler and build your faction of fighters to take on the titans. It was revealed during the Future Games Show Spring Showcase, and it's coming soon to PC. 

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

Future Games Show
